Maharashtra Covid-19 Daily Report: 14 June

#Maharashtra reported 3390 new positive cases of #Covid_19 and 120 fatalities today increasing State's tally to 1,07,958 cases including 50,978 recoveries & 3950 deaths. 
 
1632 discharges reported in the last 24 hours
